Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.30,0:00:02.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[The guys are changing.]\N[Please knock before entering.]
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.80,0:00:09.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wow. That's not gonna look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.70,0:00:12.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Quit touching me. Ow!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.97,0:00:16.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? My gym clothes are inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.65,0:00:18.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.91,0:00:20.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The boys are changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.85,0:00:25.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what to do... P.E. is about to start...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.72,0:00:28.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What... W-wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.81,0:00:50.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why? Why did she...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.35,0:00:53.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe there isn't anything Kyuuto dislikes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.85,0:00:55.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...nothing that makes her hesitate...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.82,0:01:01.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...nothing so embarrassing that it makes her cry out without realizing it...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.69,0:01:05.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...nothing she wishes could be undone but can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.89,0:01:07.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tenka toru!\N[Be victorious]
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.90,0:01:10.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Seriously?\N- We're gonna do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.07,0:01:13.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,As you all already know...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.97,0:01:18.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...this is a ritual for luck in tests dating back to when this was an all boys school.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.17,0:01:19.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We're doing this the night before the festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.57,0:01:21.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Why's it only guys?\N- That's not fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.54,0:01:25.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, Horiuchi-kun, who was top of his class...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.18,0:01:28.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...said this was stupid and refused to participate.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.62,0:01:30.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And what happened to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.42,0:01:36.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,On the day of his entrance exams he had the flu. Everything he'd worked for, up in smoke.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.09,0:01:40.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So... that's how it goes. Everyone, let's take this seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.13,0:01:45.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hey... Who had the nicest body?\N- Kageyama.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.97,0:01:47.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I saw him as the childish type.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.67,0:01:49.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But you know, he's pretty ripped...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.64,0:01:54.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to you! He's well muscled, but still slender...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.04,0:01:59.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, now, everyone. Everything will be revealed the night before the festival. There's no need to get ahead of ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Heita.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.69,0:02:06.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Fukai?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.22,0:02:09.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Only Heita had a mark.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:17.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I hate the Culture Festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.67,0:02:22.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Last year, I used my illness as an excuse and stayed home from the festival.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.97,0:02:24.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And the year before that...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.86,0:02:47.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's... It's not like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.46,0:02:49.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yay! You having fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.37,0:02:58.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Seriously, he's horrible.\N- Just mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.61,0:03:02.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Yaki-soba]
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.91,0:03:08.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The Culture Festival makes me remember things that I can usually forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.36,0:03:18.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They say you will never feel the same wind blow twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.23,0:03:22.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...there are some things you can never undo...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.43,0:03:25.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That empty, helpless feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.37,0:03:30.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. You always have hated them, haven't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.34,0:03:33.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...stuff like fireworks, and long novels...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.24,0:03:35.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you feel sad when they're over, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.04,0:03:38.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, what're you going to do about this year's festival?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.61,0:03:41.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'll stay home this year too...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.92,0:03:47.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The whole... "be victorious" thing too?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.46,0:03:49.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You think that thing really helps you pass?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.76,0:03:53.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Well, no, but...\N- Oh yeah... on the day before the festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.06,0:03:54.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...maybe I'll stay here overnight. Can I?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.76,0:03:55.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,By "here" you mean here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.86,0:03:57.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have our own "festival eve" party.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.57,0:03:58.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.50,0:04:01.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say cool stuff like, "are you depressed or something?"...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.17,0:04:02.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll borrow that bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:05.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you might be able to see the "Night Nurse."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.51,0:04:07.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? A "Night Nurse"?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:11.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,At 8 pm, a nurse comes, a woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.21,0:04:13.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She always says, "I'm the Night Nurse!"
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.95,0:04:18.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Night Nurse"... What's that mean, huh? Now it's gonna bother me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.22,0:04:20.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what it means. She's the one that says it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:23.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She says, "I'm the Night Nurse"? What's she look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.46,0:04:31.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The same wind never blows twice...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.50,0:04:37.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though I'm not in love with Shibata Kyouko anymore, don't even think about her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.71,0:04:40.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...every time I see her, my breath catches in my throat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I want to take it back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.95,0:04:50.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I remember that there are some things you can never get back...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.55,0:04:53.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...the hopelessness of that hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.49,0:04:58.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This feeling is something...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.33,0:05:01.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kyuuto probably doesn't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.44,0:05:16.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kyuuto]\NEpisode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:25.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,translation by sarujin\NQC by sayochama
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.02,0:05:32.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,GIRIGIRI FANSUBS\NNOT FOR SALE OR RENT
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.00,0:05:37.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,About the representative for the "Miss" Contest, will anyone nominate themselves?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.37,0:05:38.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.70,0:05:40.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No way. All you'd get is embarrassed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.70,0:05:42.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And Class-C's Shibata Kyouko's gonna win anyway, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.94,0:05:45.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And Shibata Kyouko's super serious about it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:48.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Apparently she's already bought clothes for the contest even though she hasn't been chosen as the rep yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.08,0:05:51.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. If you get picked, you'd have to buy new clothes too, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.98,0:05:55.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No need to worry. It'll never happen for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.25,0:05:56.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't there anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:59.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to perform too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.09,0:06:02.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're talking about cute, in our class that'd be...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:03.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kawai-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's just a pun!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.86,0:06:08.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, why don't we let our class rep do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.86,0:06:10.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's enough with the jokes already!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.50,0:06:12.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, really, no joke, have the class rep do it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.63,0:06:15.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. We have to study for exams...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.20,0:06:16.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.00,0:06:19.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I have to study too, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.14,0:06:23.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's why. This is a chance for you to take a little break, Kawai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:25.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All who think Kawai should do it...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.28,0:06:27.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.48,0:06:30.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, it's decided.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.65,0:06:35.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Turn yourself this way a little more...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.36,0:06:36.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And, smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.03,0:06:39.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.20,0:06:44.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd raise your hand too, Kageyama-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.83,0:06:46.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.07,0:06:48.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The rep for the Miss Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.64,0:06:55.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... I mean... because you're cute, Kawai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.65,0:07:00.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd make fun of me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.65,0:07:02.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:04.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.29,0:07:08.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I really do think that...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.96,0:07:18.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.20,0:07:26.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chosen to be the rep for the Miss Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.14,0:07:28.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.78,0:07:32.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If I...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.02,0:07:35.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...if I win...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.09,0:07:42.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.12,0:07:43.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.13,0:07:51.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Will you go out with me?" Is what she probably wanted to say, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.63,0:07:54.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"I've been waiting a long time."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.14,0:07:57.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Fujino.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.34,0:08:01.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujino Tsukiko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:04.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Oh. The shut-in...\N- You've heard of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.78,0:08:06.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's 3rd Year, Class-B?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.45,0:08:09.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You know... Classes are already over...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.85,0:08:12.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's okay. I like it better when there's no people.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.45,0:08:15.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise my energy gets sapped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.69,0:08:19.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.73,0:08:22.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Mark?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:24.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,On Fukai's chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a scar from his surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.17,0:08:29.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Surgery?\N- Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.84,0:08:32.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.37,0:08:34.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So that's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.08,0:08:37.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's it! That Fukai was saying he wasn't coming to the Festival...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.91,0:08:40.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, there's that "be victorious" thing, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.58,0:08:41.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you wouldn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.95,0:08:46.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. He didn't want people to see the scar on his chest...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.59,0:08:49.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly. He was worried about something like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is having a scar really that bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:58.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I think it's pretty cool...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.08,0:09:11.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.85,0:09:13.85,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's stifling in here...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.22,0:09:18.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A place like this is impossible for me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.12,0:09:22.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Fujioka!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.36,0:09:27.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nishi-senpai?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:29.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking good.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.70,0:09:35.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got this friend. He's thought up an amazing plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.70,0:09:36.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.74,0:09:38.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even without doing a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.21,0:09:41.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...money just comes rolling in.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.31,0:09:43.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.54,0:09:45.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Wanna join us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.25,0:09:52.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! No!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.29,0:09:54.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.85,0:10:24.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.12,0:10:28.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? It's all for Festival Eve?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.62,0:10:31.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Isn't that too much?\N- Well, we're staying up all night, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.67,0:10:39.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened? How'd you get this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.03,0:10:41.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It is happening to Nakao-kun too, right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.74,0:10:43.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.11,0:10:48.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao... Nakao!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.21,0:10:50.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.68,0:10:53.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.68,0:10:57.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Ow! Ow, ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.52,0:11:02.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.19,0:11:04.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,In short, all of this...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:06.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is special effects make-up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.90,0:11:10.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The eye?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.87,0:11:13.90,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Since we were doing it anyway, I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.57,0:11:16.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...we'd do it to my taste.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.94,0:11:21.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you might not do the "Victory in Exams Invocation" because you didn't want people to see your scar...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:24.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you failed your entrance exams because of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.11,0:11:26.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought that's something you can't take back, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.42,0:11:29.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then I thought I should just make scars that stand out more than yours...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.25,0:11:32.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you go this far for me? ...going out of your way to make scars and stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.82,0:11:35.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You came running to help me because you thought I was in trouble, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.06,0:11:38.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you shouldn't be running...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.97,0:11:45.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm really exhausted...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.40,0:11:46.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It seems like...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.20,0:11:50.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...there's this feeling like I have to be in that "Victory in Exams Invocation," you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.24,0:11:52.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... But after I'm done for the day, I'll come back.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.94,0:11:56.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to see that "Night Nurse," right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:58.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nakao's a good guy, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.45,0:12:00.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.08,0:12:02.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.39,0:12:13.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Bang.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.37,0:12:20.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.42,0:12:44.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's a charm to ward off evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.76,0:12:47.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything more happens I'm going to have to take some time off of school.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:54.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Is it all right to dispose of money?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.10,0:12:55.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's not throwing it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.07,0:12:57.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's an offering.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.37,0:13:01.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka-kun disposed of some too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.34,0:13:03.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really? He made a wish at a shrine too?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.75,0:13:05.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,30,000 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,30,000 yen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:16.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So... you can do things like this too...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.37,0:13:25.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've got this friend...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.80,0:13:27.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He's thought up this amazing plan...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:29.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A plan?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.24,0:13:31.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- What?\N- Even without doing a thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.01,0:13:34.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...money comes rolling in.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.38,0:13:37.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad! That job's gotta be something dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.65,0:13:39.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Think it over.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:43.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are we gonna do, Fujioka?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.39,0:13:49.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We will tell him not to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.59,0:13:53.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... Well, yes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.80,0:13:55.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't just say, "don't do it."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.60,0:14:00.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like we can take care of Fujioka's living expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.37,0:14:06.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If he had money, this would end without Fujioka having to do dangerous work?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.17,0:14:08.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well... For now anyway...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.75,0:14:17.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,30,000, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.59,0:14:26.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.00,0:14:31.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We will have everyone dispose of their money here, for Fukioka's sake.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.33,0:14:33.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Everyone," who?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.67,0:14:36.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The people I meet starting now. Everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.67,0:14:40.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please dispose of some.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.58,0:14:42.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Me too?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:49.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I just really can't... I'll make sure to return the money.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.72,0:14:52.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You used it all already?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.19,0:14:55.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're pretty careless with your money, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.56,0:14:59.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You've got a little brother, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.16,0:15:02.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What're you gonna do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.96,0:15:05.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Guess there's no helping it, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.21,0:15:16.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Think it over carefully, one more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.59,0:15:27.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That comes to 440 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.73,0:15:37.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend is poking his nose into dangerous business.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.00,0:15:41.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, dispose of your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.24,0:15:45.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, dispose of your money.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.21,0:15:47.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Money?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think you could lend me some?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.78,0:15:51.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't really ask mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.88,0:15:54.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Another idol?\N- No.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.52,0:15:57.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Clothes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.92,0:15:59.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Clothes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.86,0:16:01.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you stupid?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.26,0:16:03.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Clothes aren't important enough to borrow money for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.63,0:16:08.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chosen as the representative.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.26,0:16:09.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Representative?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.36,0:16:11.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,From my class, for the Miss Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:12.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.20,0:16:15.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone as ugly as you would never be in a "Miss" Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.80,0:16:17.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I really was chosen.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.64,0:16:20.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Then they're just harassing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.61,0:16:23.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They make the ugly girl feel good, then laugh at her.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.78,0:16:26.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You get excited, even go so far as to buy clothes...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.15,0:16:27.42,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How stupid are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.15,0:16:31.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't even think about entering that thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.90,0:16:42.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You should enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.50,0:16:49.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.57,0:16:53.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No... It's true, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.68,0:16:54.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.24,0:17:00.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Someone like me... It's only because I work so hard at studying that people treat me like one of them...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.98,0:17:05.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Just like my older brother said, I'm ugly, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.19,0:17:09.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It could be that this "brother" of yours is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.00,0:17:17.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai-san, you're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.27,0:17:19.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No, I can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way that can be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.71,0:17:26.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:30.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,So, you won't believe what I say...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.76,0:17:42.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.99,0:17:46.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yamamoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:49.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...it isn't that I don't trust you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.20,0:17:54.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.90,0:17:57.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...but I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.67,0:18:00.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Because, I'm...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.51,0:18:01.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.31,0:18:05.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You've come all this way...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.91,0:18:08.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...without saying wrong things are wrong, haven't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.42,0:18:15.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't say, "that's wrong"...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.79,0:18:18.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...the "wrong" things become the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.73,0:18:24.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Unless you say it as loud as you can...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.04,0:18:29.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,After all, no one else will say it for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.41,0:18:32.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it. Scream it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.84,0:18:36.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "I am beautiful."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.21,0:18:40.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who cares if people make fun of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.78,0:18:43.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Get out of my way!\N- What's with her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.32,0:18:46.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Say, "it isn't true," as loud as you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.89,0:18:51.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A friend has poked his nose into dangerous business.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.13,0:18:54.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.61,0:19:15.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll just keep on screaming...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.28,0:19:18.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have love. I don't have money.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.22,0:19:22.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a proud ne'er-do-well
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.29,0:19:26.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.90,0:19:32.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,They're beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.97,0:19:36.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're sure you don't mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure. I'm not gonna wear them again.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.91,0:19:40.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.49,0:19:56.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.96,0:20:02.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.73,0:20:06.37,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am not ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.08,0:20:15.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kyuuto?\N- Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.28,0:20:17.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She just got back... tattered and worn-out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.18,0:20:18.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Worn-out?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.26,0:20:35.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She was serious...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.71,0:20:49.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shikahamabashi High School is about to begin the Festival Eve events.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.41,0:20:55.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All senior boys, please begin preparations for the "Victory in Exams Invocation."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.38,0:21:00.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I been tellin' you! The way you talk's weird!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:02.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Say it proper. Proper. Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.99,0:21:03.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Go on.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:05.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your money...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.73,0:21:07.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your money...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.00,0:21:09.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your money...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.06,0:21:12.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Your money...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.75,0:21:26.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.75,0:21:30.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Miss... Ow, hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.35,0:21:33.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hot... Hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.73,0:21:46.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shall I bring in some ice? Miss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.27,0:21:48.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.24,0:21:55.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But... What if she's actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.78,0:21:57.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...a crane or something...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.66,0:22:15.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sensei, may I borrow the yellow paint?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.93,0:22:17.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, go ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.87,0:22:21.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hello. Please excuse me for intruding.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.27,0:22:22.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Hello.\N- What're you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.97,0:22:27.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean? You said you'd be late, so I brought some ohagi...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.48,0:22:29.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Thank you so much!\N- Why'd you bring ohagi?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.44,0:22:34.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- I am his mother...\N- Okay. I get it! Thank you. Let's go home, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:38.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not leaving yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.62,0:22:40.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you had enough already?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.09,0:22:44.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Back then... it was because of you we didn't make it to Koshien, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.73,0:22:47.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That again? I've heard it enough already...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.76,0:22:51.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,To make a mistake like that at such an important moment...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.97,0:22:57.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was so incredibly embarrassed...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.84,0:23:00.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I didn't think I could live, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.48,0:23:07.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...it was unexpectedly easy to keep living, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.75,0:23:12.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,For both me and you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.52,0:23:15.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.53,0:23:20.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What do I do? It's impossible now. Impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:23.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The dress I borrowed was put in the wash...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.00,0:23:30.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It must mean... that I shouldn't be in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:32.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Right? I mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.04,0:23:35.04,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...it isn't as if anyone will be put out if I don't enter.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.21,0:23:37.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.41,0:23:40.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll go tell them I'm not participating.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.15,0:23:46.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do something about the clothes... okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:51.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like my brother said.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.66,0:23:56.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It was wrong of me to enter at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.83,0:24:01.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what you may say, Yamamoto-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.47,0:24:04.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I...am ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.74,0:24:08.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you going to believe your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.98,0:24:12.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Or are you going to believe in yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.12,0:24:18.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you going to live your life believing in?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.26,0:24:26.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe in myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:38.77,0:24:41.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- I just push here?\N- That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.24,0:24:43.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,How simple!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:45.15,0:24:47.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It'd be nice if people were that simple too...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:47.75,0:24:49.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.72,0:24:50.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.42,0:24:55.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...words don't get through... and I can't give a hug...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:56.69,0:24:58.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do at a time like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.53,0:25:04.13,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.47,0:25:05.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...is passion.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.50,0:25:12.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You see... Right here, you can feel this heat simmering, and soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.31,0:25:14.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...pop! The lid will come flying off.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:14.28,0:25:17.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And it will land, clink, with the person you're trying to reach.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:17.38,0:25:18.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It'll hit its target that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.98,0:25:23.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't think about aiming, just hope for its flying.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.35,0:25:27.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Like this... Pop!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:34.33,0:25:36.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Be victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.33,0:25:40.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Be victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:42.54,0:25:44.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Be victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.04,0:25:46.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Has it started?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:49.34,0:25:50.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nishi?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.45,0:25:55.08,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're looking good!
Dialogue: 0,0:25:55.92,0:26:00.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The school is doing the same old ridiculous stuff I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:00.56,0:26:01.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose so.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:02.72,0:26:05.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right! I have to give them back, don't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:05.59,0:26:07.43,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.93,0:26:11.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:12.70,0:26:15.57,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need this stuff after all this time...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.57,0:26:17.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.47,0:26:20.31,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here. This one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:21.88,0:26:25.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You know... This was the one thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.25,0:26:30.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...you always tried your hardest in.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.22,0:26:33.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Be victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:35.02,0:26:37.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Be victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.83,0:26:41.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Be victorious!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:46.57,0:26:49.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There she is! I found her!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.10,0:26:52.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kawai-san, you have to come!\N- This way! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.71,0:26:57.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. Here we are.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.48,0:27:00.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.18,0:27:03.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.89,0:27:07.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:08.69,0:27:11.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.69,0:27:15.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.30,0:27:16.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.66,0:27:19.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:19.93,0:27:24.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He's risking his entrance exams to say that. Lift your head and listen to it, for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:24.44,0:27:27.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.11,0:27:30.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.78,0:27:34.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.98,0:27:38.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Will you give this back to Kageyama-kun for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.75,0:27:42.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kawai is beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.49,0:27:46.46,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- The Miss Contest is about to start!\N- Seriously? Better get moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.41,0:28:05.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.05,0:28:07.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't tell me... it reached her?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.26,0:28:21.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was chosen to be the rep for the Miss Contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.20,0:28:30.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're leaving without watching the Miss Contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.61,0:28:34.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I promised someone else, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.08,0:28:36.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Watch, for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:39.31,0:28:41.92,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like anything will change if I watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.25,0:28:43.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.29,0:28:47.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even though this moment will only happen this once...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.54,0:29:10.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.31,0:29:12.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...uniforms from other schools?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.98,0:29:17.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We'll accessorize and coordinate, and create a one-of-a-kind uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.59,0:29:23.99,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Sorry. Looks like I'm gonna be a little longer.]
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.80,0:29:35.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.20,0:29:39.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Next up, from class 3-B, Kawai Emiko-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.11,0:29:40.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Here she is!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.01,0:29:47.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.47,0:30:08.14,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Amazing...\N- We've been waiting!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.21,0:30:16.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I am Kawai, from 3rd year, class B.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.24,0:30:19.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be singing, "The Wind."
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.62,0:30:33.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single person...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.06,0:30:36.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...sets out on their journey alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.20,0:30:42.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single person...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.00,0:30:45.01,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...looks back at the home they've left.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.11,0:30:50.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Feeling just a little bit lonely...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.24,0:30:53.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if you turn and look back...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:54.75,0:31:02.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...all that will be there is the wind blowing.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.66,0:31:07.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single person...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:07.80,0:31:10.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...stumbles in their lives.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:11.93,0:31:16.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Every single person, has their dream crushed...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.44,0:31:19.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...and turns to look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:20.78,0:31:25.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Dry sycamore leaves dance...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.11,0:31:28.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...on this winter road.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.28,0:31:33.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,At the sound of the sycamore leaves falling...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.72,0:31:36.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I turn and look back.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.86,0:31:45.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I hear "please, come home," and turn back...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.17,0:31:48.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,All that there will be is the wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.84,0:31:54.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That day... If I had just smiled and said, "it's fine," after you shook me off your arm...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:56.41,0:31:59.35,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...do you think we'd still be together, even now?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:59.88,0:32:01.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If I won the Miss Contest...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.58,0:32:05.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I thought I might be able to get that back.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.96,0:32:10.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Of course we can get it back"...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.09,0:32:13.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...will you say that for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.80,0:32:16.56,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...even if it's a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.73,0:32:21.00,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If we started dating again...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:24.71,0:32:27.47,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...would that mean that we'd gone back and fixed things?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:30.68,0:32:32.98,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I know that's not what it would be.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:36.45,0:32:38.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:40.05,0:32:41.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...that it wouldn't be. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.23,0:32:45.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Getting something back"...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:48.60,0:32:49.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...probably means...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.00,0:32:56.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...being able to move on to the next thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:07.72,0:33:09.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shibata Kyouko-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.55,0:33:11.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand-by, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.55,0:33:12.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.73,0:33:25.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Shake my hand off...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.64,0:33:28.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...and go.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.14,0:33:33.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, and we'll take back everything. Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:47.99,0:33:49.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Now...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.62,0:33:51.29,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...we're even.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.70,0:33:55.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.41,0:34:16.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Please, look out for my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.15,0:34:19.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Huh? You're leaving already?\N- I have somewhere to go...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.72,0:34:21.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! I have one of these too.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.79,0:34:22.96,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.13,0:34:28.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.40,0:34:30.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong? Chiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.70,0:34:33.30,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiro licked that amulet, and now...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.54,0:34:37.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- That's because it wards against evil spirits!\N- What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:37.54,0:34:40.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If anything other than a human touches it...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.67,0:34:45.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...they say that whatever it is will suddenly vanish from this world, taken out like garbage.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.41,0:34:48.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Anything that isn't human?\N- Well, Chiro-chan is an animal, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:48.52,0:34:51.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Chiro-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.79,0:34:55.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? You mean you mean nothing not human should touch it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.22,0:34:57.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do? I gave one to Kyuuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.32,0:34:58.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? Kyuu-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.83,0:35:00.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's really that effective?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.16,0:35:03.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's extraordinarily effective.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.80,0:35:11.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,A lightning bolt struck.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.97,0:35:14.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It couldn't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.24,0:35:16.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...not on Kyuuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.58,0:35:22.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Come on now, get back. Stand back, I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.85,0:35:29.72,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.72,0:35:31.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- Kyuuto!\N- Get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:31.83,0:35:35.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down! There's no one in there. That's just a machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.23,0:35:38.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto! Kyuuto...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.41,0:35:48.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:58.45,0:35:59.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:20.71,0:36:22.24,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.45,0:36:34.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.99,0:36:40.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.23,0:36:47.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.91,0:37:00.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.12,0:37:04.55,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be looking after you tonight. My name is Kagawa. Pleased to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.55,0:37:07.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What? I mean... Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.52,0:37:10.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the "I'm the Night Nurse" person?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.69,0:37:14.63,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. Kanai-san. Didn't you hear? She got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.63,0:37:17.93,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She's probably in Italy right now. I'm so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:22.64,0:37:25.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,We're home!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.71,0:37:28.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly, Tou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.68,0:37:30.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This is how he gets when we leave him alone...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.81,0:37:33.48,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you sleep there, you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.45,0:37:35.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.55,0:37:39.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The crane...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.29,0:37:41.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the crane?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.76,0:37:43.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.12,0:37:45.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There was a crane here!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.06,0:37:47.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,- A robotic Crane Wife.\N- You drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.49,0:37:50.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No! She... She was in that room!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.36,0:37:53.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She had her wings spread, like this, but they were mechanical.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.97,0:37:55.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.70,0:37:57.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,No! Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.27,0:38:01.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's nothing there.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.18,0:38:02.44,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:02.44,0:38:03.54,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You're kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:03.54,0:38:04.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me a sec...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.28,0:38:09.45,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She... She was right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.45,0:38:12.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The machine was flashing...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:12.25,0:38:13.62,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You were dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.62,0:38:15.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.09,0:38:16.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You drank too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.26,0:38:22.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:26.57,0:38:27.80,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fujioka!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.14,0:38:35.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto collected this for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:36.84,0:38:39.38,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,She said it's so you won't get involved in anything dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:40.81,0:38:43.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. We overheard you and Senpai talking.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.69,0:38:49.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Loose change like this... isn't going to change anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.92,0:38:52.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That might be true, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.43,0:38:54.53,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Look...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:54.93,0:38:57.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I've told you this has nothing to do with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:00.67,0:39:01.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:02.34,0:39:03.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not my problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.31,0:39:08.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,But I don't like it when people crush other people.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:10.21,0:39:11.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't like it either, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.25,0:39:15.78,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Standing by silently... watching someone get crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:16.45,0:39:17.95,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You hate it, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.02,0:39:23.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Nishi-senpai...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.16,0:39:26.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...wouldn't do that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.60,0:39:33.10,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, what is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.93,0:39:36.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,You really are an idiot, aren't you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.97,0:39:38.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The money you tossed...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.14,0:39:41.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...I was the one who picked it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.04,0:39:44.11,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:44.51,0:39:46.75,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just like he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.48,0:39:50.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I was going to crush you under my heel.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.02,0:39:55.09,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Being made to carry all this junk...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.69,0:39:58.79,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...lies just can't make it through this stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.20,0:40:10.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.22,0:40:31.12,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kubo-kun? Sorry to keep you waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.19,0:40:33.26,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Who's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.53,0:40:41.97,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Fukai-kun asked me to come play games all night in his place.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:43.50,0:40:45.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Which do you want to settle first?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.77,0:40:49.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Heita hates endings.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.51,0:40:50.64,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Really...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.41,0:40:53.58,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And because he's afraid of endings...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.05,0:40:56.68,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...he's not good at starting things.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:57.15,0:41:00.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you can't live that way, can you?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.19,0:41:02.39,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Humans die, 100%...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.39,0:41:03.69,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone... Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.09,0:41:06.36,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone knows that. That's why you live.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:06.36,0:41:08.33,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Tell Heita that.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.67,0:41:15.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Did I die? Here... Did I die?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.20,0:41:17.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. You died perfectly.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.67,0:41:21.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no, no, no. Bring me back to life.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.11,0:41:25.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I ended up spending the whole time at school...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:43.13,0:41:45.27,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry! Are you okay? You aren't hurt?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.70,0:41:48.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.40,0:41:51.17,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Where on earth did she learn that?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.47,0:41:57.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Guys! Quit goofing off!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.05,0:42:06.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[You can still take it back. Hang in there!]
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.46,0:42:10.52,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Come back...]
Dialogue: 0,0:42:10.52,0:42:12.76,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[There's no such thing as too late. Please, don't give up.]
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.76,0:42:14.59,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Just a little more! Keep trying!]
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.46,0:42:17.03,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,The same wind...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.66,0:42:19.23,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...will never blow twice.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.30,0:42:23.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,And in the midst of that...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:24.87,0:42:26.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...we live.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:47.89,0:42:50.73,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. Screaming and crying.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.40,0:42:53.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the first time I'd seen something like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.30,0:42:57.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It kinda creeped me out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.04,0:42:59.87,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...somehow, it was moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.87,0:43:01.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Heita]
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.21,0:43:06.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I had a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:08.65,0:43:11.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto was human...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.18,0:43:12.82,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...and I was a robot.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.32,0:43:17.89,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,When I asked, sobbing, why I wasn't a human...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.03,0:43:22.06,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...Kyuuto came to my side and said this...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:23.50,0:43:25.70,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Being human or not..."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:26.53,0:43:28.77,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...that stuff doesn't matter."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:31.74,0:43:37.28,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Right now, you and I, Heita, we're becoming human."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:38.21,0:43:40.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Being worried for by others..."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:41.21,0:43:43.88,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"...worrying about others... We can do that."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:44.42,0:43:47.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"We are becoming people that others can love."
Dialogue: 0,0:43:48.36,0:43:50.16,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,"Isn't that enough?"
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.56,0:43:55.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Kyuuto's words were so kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.76,0:44:00.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...even in my dream, I sobbed uncontrollably.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:01.84,0:44:04.20,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kaidan no katasumi ni...]\NIn a corner, on the stairs...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.20,0:44:06.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...suwari uzukumaru no ano hito ni...]\N...that person cowering, crouched...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.84,0:44:08.91,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...nani ga atta n darou]\N...I wonder what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.91,0:44:12.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Ittai nani wo mitekita n darou]\NWhat did that person see?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.25,0:44:14.21,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Hitogomi no naka de...]\NIn a crowd of people...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.21,0:44:17.05,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...niramiau danjou no aida ni...]\N...that man and woman glare at each other...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:17.05,0:44:19.19,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...nani ga okottarou]\N...I wonder what happened between them.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:19.19,0:44:26.49,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Ittai donna jijou ga atta n darou]\NWhat circumstances led them there?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.77,0:44:34.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Itsuka boku wo yobidashita...]\NOnce, you called me outside...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.94,0:44:37.67,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...sensei ga donatteta sono scene ha...]\N...and the teacher yelled. That scene...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.67,0:44:39.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...donna dattarou]\N...I wonder what it looked like.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.34,0:44:42.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Ittai boku ha nani wo shitta n darou]\NWhat on earth did I learn from it?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:42.84,0:44:45.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Itsu kara ka tsuzuiteru...]\NOn the other side...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.18,0:44:47.71,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...sensou no hate ni donna koto ga...]\N...of this war that's lasted since who knows when...
Dialogue: 0,0:44:47.71,0:44:49.65,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...matteru n darou]\N...I wonder what waits for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:49.65,0:44:57.22,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Soushite boku ni nani ga dekiru n darou]\NAnd what can I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:58.26,0:45:00.86,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Koto no shinsou ha nani mo...]\NThe truth of things...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.86,0:45:03.40,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...shitteiru you de shirienai...]\N...we feel like we know, but we can't learn...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:03.40,0:45:05.50,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Sore demo dou ni ka kou ni ka...]\NEven so, somehow or another...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:05.50,0:45:08.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[...ikiteita naka ga nai]\N...It's like we were never here.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.60,0:45:11.07,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Muda ga atteba tarirarenai]\NIt's not enough to meet with futility...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:11.07,0:45:13.84,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Demo shinjirareru mono mo sukunai]\NBut there are too few things to believe in...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:13.84,0:45:18.61,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Tada hitotsu tashika na no ha boku no kimochi]\NThe only certain thing is my feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.61,0:45:21.51,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kimi no sono koe wo kikashite yo]\NLet me hear that voice of yours
Dialogue: 0,0:45:21.51,0:45:24.15,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Shinjireru mono ga soko ni aru yo]\NThat's where I find something to believe in
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.15,0:45:28.32,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Tada hitotsu tashika na no ha omae to no toki]\NThe only certain thing is my time with you...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.32,0:45:33.83,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,[Kimi ga suki]\NI love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:33.83,0:45:37.66,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,This world is made up of stuff that doesn't matter and stuff you can't do anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.66,0:45:40.60,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,He is a man who has no mercy for others.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.60,0:45:42.34,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be you, Sensei!
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.34,0:45:43.94,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no such thing as "forever" in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:43.94,0:45:45.74,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,Everything ends, one day.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.74,0:45:47.81,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it. She isn't human.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.28,0:45:53.41,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,If you let go, it's all over.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.41,0:45:55.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,I want to say the things that I think, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.25,0:45:57.18,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...it'll put the people I'm talking to in a bind too, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.18,0:45:59.25,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,O-Tentou-sama is always with you, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:45:59.25,0:46:03.02,dtdw,,0000,0000,0000,,...without effort, not a single grain of rice shall grow
